<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to Babak Marketplace</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .logo {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #2563eb;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .title {
            color: #1f2937;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .content {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #2563eb;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .button:hover {
            background-color: #1d4ed8;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #6b7280;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .feature-box {
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">BABAK</div>
            <div style="color: #6b7280;">Marketplace</div>
        </div>
        
        <h1 class="title">Welcome to Babak Marketplace! ðŸŽ‰</h1>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hello {{name}},</p>
            
            <p>Congratulations! Your email has been verified and your account is now active. Welcome to Syria's premier online marketplace where you can buy and sell everything from electronics to real estate.</p>
            
            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="{{loginUrl}}" class="button">Start Exploring</a>
            </div>
            
            <div class="feature-box">
                <h3 style="color: #1f2937; margin-top: 0;">What you can do now:</h3>
                <ul style="margin: 0;">
                    <li><strong>Browse thousands of listings</strong> - Find exactly what you're looking for</li>
                    <li><strong>Post your own ads</strong> - Sell items quickly and easily</li>
                    <li><strong>Connect with buyers and sellers</strong> - Safe messaging system</li>
                    <li><strong>Save favorites</strong> - Keep track of items you're interested in</li>
                    <li><strong>Get notifications</strong> - Stay updated on your listings and messages</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <h3 style="color: #1f2937;">Getting Started Tips:</h3>
            <ol>
                <li><strong>Complete your profile</strong> - Add a photo and description to build trust</li>
                <li><strong>Browse categories</strong> - Explore what's available in your area</li>
                <li><strong>Post your first listing</strong> - Take clear photos and write detailed descriptions</li>
                <li><strong>Stay safe</strong> - Meet in public places and trust your instincts</li>
            </ol>
            
            <p>If you have any questions or need help getting started, don't hesitate to reach out to our support team.</p>
            
            <p>Happy buying and selling!</p>
            <p>The Babak Marketplace Team</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Need help? Contact us at <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}">{{supportEmail}}</a></p>
            <p>&copy; 2025 Babak Marketplace. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
